# Force LF on all shell scripts and CMake/Docker files used by the M2-C
# cross-build, so a Windows checkout (core.autocrlf=true) does not turn
# their line endings into CRLF and break the Linux `/usr/bin/env bash\r`
# shebang inside the libegd-arm64:builder container.
*.sh             text eol=lf
*.cmake          text eol=lf
Dockerfile*      text eol=lf
**/cross-wrappers/* text eol=lf
